text: Neighbors is a 2014 American comedy movie. It is about a couple with a baby moving who have partying students move next door to them. Rose Byrne plays Kelly Radner. Seth Rogen plays Mac Radner, Zac Efron plays Teddy Sanders. The movie received positive reviews. This movie was released in May 2014. It is followed by Neighbors 2: Sorority Rising.
